{"tid":306713,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想同俾帽我帶既你講","createTime":"2017-07-02T18:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T19:34:26.000Z","uid":23568,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0fedfb468de87ba1babb6a29fc267111f1f3643","tid":306713,"uid":23568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:25:05.000Z","msg":"當初被帶帽 選擇左原諒<br />\n好快你就斬哂欖<br />\n之後幾年後都係相安無事<br />\n你亦係大家眼中的一百分男友<br />\n<br />\n到左談婚論嫁果一刻先發現自己唔得<br />\n所以選擇左分手<br />\n<br />\n知道你係好後悔 但係有啲野做左就做左<br />\n希望你以後對下一個女仔好啲啦<br />\n<br />\n多謝你對我的好 同照顧<br />\n聽到你仲未放低我 都唔知應唔應該開心<br />\n可惜我地返唔到轉頭喇<br />\n<br />\n希望你以後會好好啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb98df29e08723d26d3bcbd070f73c75291815f","tid":306713,"uid":3688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:26:14.000Z","msg":"錯不在你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9d6f85fc56c76ecee5c9507d6a0b9a1ea1da71","tid":306713,"uid":23568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錯不在你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係到講完 舒服哂 又唔想打擾到佢"},{"pid":"ae2f287ca6d9e9d14349c10be618e41c1f781f7c","tid":306713,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:44:10.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eeac862fb913508ad7b746c7b7fe477d790d225","tid":306713,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:45:09.000Z","msg":"你個夠應景"},{"pid":"74370003c5c34557f1f0ba05ccf08d4e741bcb03","tid":306713,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:45:09.000Z","msg":"你個夠應景"},{"pid":"0286c8a1b28bd7426fa53e62ef61ecb07c1f27c7","tid":306713,"uid":41432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:45:35.000Z","msg":"我以為係歌詞"},{"pid":"6650d5b05b31b977c2ccf9f137b75971